high_descs: Turn around. Reach the refrigerator. Turn right, go ahead and then turn left. Go straight to the sink.
Grab the tomato.
Turn around, go to the pan and turn right. Approach the pan.
Open the fridge doors. Put the tomato in. Place it on top of the pan.
Take out the pan with the tomato. Close the refrigerator.
Turn around. Reach the wall. Turn left, get to the countertop.
Place the pan and tomato on the left side over the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Find a tomato and a pan and place them on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn around to reach the kitchen and head to the sink.
Pick up the tomato from the sink.
Turn around to reach the pan.
Put the tomato in the pan in the fridge.
Pick up the pan from the fridge.
Turn right to reach the countertop on the left of the sink.
Put the pan on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate on the tomato on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the red tomato from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the pan.
Put the tomato on the pan in the fridge.
Pick up the pan with the tomato from the fridge.
Turn right and walk back to the kitchen countertop.
Put the pan with tomato down on the countertop just left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pan with tomato on the kitchen countertop
